{"prompt": "Generate a website for a video game studio. The website should be clean and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Crimson Studios</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #f4f4f4;\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        header {\n            background-color: #c0392b; /* Brand Red */\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 2rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 3rem;\n        }\n        main {\n            padding: 2rem;\n            max-width: 1000px;\n            margin: 2rem auto;\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        section {\n            margin-bottom: 2rem;\n        }\n        h2 {\n            color: #c0392b; /* Brand Red */\n            border-bottom: 2px solid #c0392b;\n            padding-bottom: 0.5rem;\n            margin-bottom: 1rem;\n        }\n        .game-list {\n            list-style: none;\n            padding: 0;\n        }\n        .game-list li {\n            margin-bottom: 1rem;\n            padding: 1rem;\n            background-color: #fefefe;\n            border-left: 5px solid #c0392b; /* Brand Red */\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .game-list li:hover {\n            background-color: #fbe9e7; /* Lighter shade of Red */\n        }\n        footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 2rem 0;\n            margin-top: 2rem;\n            background-color: #333;\n            color: #ffffff;\n        }\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <h1>Crimson Studios</h1>\n        <p>Crafting Worlds, One Pixel at a Time</p>\n    </header>\n    <main>\n        <section id=\"about\">\n            <h2>About Us</h2>\n            <p>Crimson Studios is an independent video game development company dedicated to creating immersive and engaging experiences. We believe in the power of storytelling and innovative gameplay to captivate players and leave a lasting impression.</p>\n        </section>\n        <section id=\"games\">\n            <h2>Our Games</h2>\n            <ul class=\"game-list\">\n                <li>\n                    <h3>Shadows of Eldoria</h3>\n                    <p>A dark fantasy RPG where you explore ancient ruins, battle mythical creatures, and uncover a forgotten prophecy.</p>\n                </li>\n                <li>\n                    <h3>Galactic Odyssey</h3>\n                    <p>Embark on an epic space adventure, charting unknown galaxies, trading goods, and engaging in thrilling dogfights.</p>\n                </li>\n                <li>\n                    <h3>Pixel Puzzler</h3>\n                    <p>A charming 2D puzzle platformer that challenges your logic and reflexes with inventive level design.</p>\n                </li>\n            </ul>\n        </section>\n        <section id=\"contact\">\n            <h2>Contact Us</h2>\n            <p>Have questions or want to collaborate? Reach out to us!</p>\n            <p>Email: <a href=\"mailto:info@crimsonstudios.com\">info@crimsonstudios.com</a></p>\n            <p>Follow us on social media!</p>\n            </section>\n    </main>\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Crimson Studios. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n</body>\n</html>"}